quot;Courier New&quot;; color: rgb(224, 238, 224); background-color: rgb(16, 48, 64);\" class=\"source\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;link</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">rel=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;shortcut icon&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">href=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;&#39;;bloginfo(&#39;template_url\');;echo \'/images/favicon.ico&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br></div>\r\n\r\n以上2行代码选其一，根据主题选择。\r\n\r\n保存，之后刷新博客，在地址栏左边即出现了自己的ICO。','给WordPress制作图标','','publish','open','open','','wordpress-icomake','','','2012-02-19 16:54:41','2012-02-19 08:54:41','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=409',0,'post','',0),(417,1,'2011-05-26 09:50:43','2011-05-26 01:50:43','偶然在Google reader里订阅到朋友里看到“千人挑战”的信息，那我也来凑热闹。\r\n\r\n这次活动是拿能福的互助推广活动，让更多的博主加入到拿能福中成为拿铁，同时会给加入的童鞋们以50RMB（50,000/1000）的回报。原文是这样的“我们的目标是召集更多的博主成功注册并加入拿福能，将人民币50,000元平分给活动开始后前1000名加入的每一位博主（每人50元）！”这儿就是分钱了，有朋友看到这篇文章的，一起来吧！\r\n\r\n“拿福能”（Nuffnang.com）是亚太地区首家领先的博客广告社区。我们的在线平台将广告商的图文或者视频广告成功发布到超过100,000篇博客上，并通过他们传播到各种领域。Nuffnang.com目前在四个国家设立了办事处，分别是新加坡、马来西亚、菲律宾和澳大利亚。所以，千人挑战值得挑战。\r\n\r\n具体参与方法看这里：<a href=\"http://www.nuffnang.com.cn/blog/2011/05/23/challenge-1000/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nuffnang.com.cn/blog/2011/05/23/challenge-1000/</a>','千人挑战','','publish','open','open','','challenge-1000','','','2012-02-19 16:57:09','2012-02-19 08:57:09','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=417',0,'post','',3),(424,1,'2011-05-28 10:07:30','2011-05-28 02:07:30','毕设迫在眉睫，但是好像没怎么搞。于是得下功夫了。\r\n\r\n不知不觉，才没多少时间，某大神已经通过oDesk赚了$600+了。也可能是gDev发现没人给他们干活所以又找上我这种水人了，然后是还要1个星期的试用，试用合格报酬丰富，但是试用不合格就什么都没有。于是下定决心做一做，反正水也就水一个星期。\r\n\r\n博主哪，个人水平需要提高哪！','开始忙碌','','publish','open','open','','begin-busy','','','2012-02-19 16:38:27','2012-02-19 08:38:27','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=424',0,'post','',4),(426,1,'2011-05-28 21:12:40','2011-05-28 13:12:40','gDev来信说了一堆，给了一堆帐号密码，我十分不爽，等我研究完那些帐号密码干什么用的，一个星期早就过去了，我就不用做事了。\r\n\r\n没办法，还是跟着学点。反正也是水一水。等待下载cent-os的虚拟机文件的时间，看了看ant是什么。另外还有oracle，这东西也没有用过，不过过两天再看了。把看到的和自己简单测试的笔记一下。\r\n\r\n<h3>ant是什么？</h3>\r\n\r\nGoogle.com.hk里面输入ant，翻第一个中文介绍速度看了下，我于是从<a href=\"http://www.chedong.com/tech/ant.html\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a>学到了ant就是makefile。\r\n\r\n<h3>ant安装</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>gDev使用的是1.6.2，于是从<a href=\"http://olex.openlogic.com/content/openlogic/ant/1.6.2/ant-1.6.2-windows-bin.zip\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>下载了Windows版本。</li>\r\n	<li>解压到任何一个自己喜欢的目录，如我的是D:\\Java\\ant-1.6.2</li>\r\n	<li>添加系统环境变量到ANT_HOME，值为D:\\Java\\ant-1.6.2，将系统环境变量Path值增加;%ANT_HOME%\\bin。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>ant使用示例</h3>\r\n\r\n参考<a href=\"http://www.chengxurensheng.com/htm/2011/2/820.htm\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>建立java源文件。如新建test.ant.HelloWorld.java包:\r\n     <div style=\"background:#fdfdfd;color:black;\"><u>Java语言</u>: <a href=\"http://fayaa.com/code/view/19951/\">Codee#19951</a></div>\r\n     <div style=\"font-family: &quot;Consolas&quot;,&quot;Lucida Console&quot;,&quot;Courier New&quot;; color: rgb(224, 238, 224); background-color: rgb(16, 48, 64);\" class=\"source\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">package</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">test</span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">ant</span>;<br> <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 216, 230);\">public</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 216, 230);\">class</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">HelloWorld</span> <br> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">{</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 216, 230);\">public</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 216, 230);\">static</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(173, 216, 230);\">void</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">main</span>(<span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">String</span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">[]</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">args</span>) <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">{</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">System</span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">out</span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">println</span>(<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);<br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">}</span><br> <span style=\"color: rgb(224, 238, 224);\">}</span><br></div>\r\n\r\n  \r\n当然HelloWorld.java放置的目录格式[home]/test/ant/HelloWorld.java。</li>\r\n	<li>在[home]同级目录新建build.xml文件，内容为：\r\n     <div style=\"background:#fdfdfd;color:black;\"><u>XML语言</u>: <a href=\"http://fayaa.com/code/view/19952/\">Codee#19952</a></div>\r\n     <div style=\"font-family: &quot;Consolas&quot;,&quot;Lucida Console&quot;,&quot;Courier New&quot;; color: rgb(224, 238, 224); background-color: rgb(16, 48, 64);\" class=\"source\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(141, 182, 205);\">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?&gt;</span><br> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;project</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;HelloWorld&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">default=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;run&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">basedir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;.&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;property</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;src&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">value=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;src&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;property</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;dest&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">value=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;classes&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;property</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;hello_jar&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">value=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;hello.jar&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;init&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;mkdir</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">dir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${dest}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;compile&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">depends=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;init&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;javac</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">srcdir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${src}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">destdir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${dest}&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;build&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">depends=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;compile&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;jar</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">jarfile=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${hello_jar}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">basedir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${dest}&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;manifest&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;attribute</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;Main-Class&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">value=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;test.ant.HelloWorld&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/manifest&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/jar&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;run&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">depends=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;build&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;java</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">classname=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;test.ant.HelloWorld&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">classpath=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${hello_jar}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;clean&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;delete</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">dir=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${dest}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;delete</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">file=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;${hello_jar}&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;target</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">name=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;rerun&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">depends=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;clean,run&quot;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;ant</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">target=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;clean&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;ant</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 205, 155);\">target=</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 229, 238);\">&quot;run&quot;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">/&gt;</span><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/target&gt;</span><br> <span style=\"color: rgb(144, 238, 144);\">&lt;/project&gt;</span><br></div>\r\n\r\n  \r\n</li>\r\n	<li>命令行进入[home]目录，输入ant即执行，在[home]目录则生成了。ant build编译生成jar文件，ant rerun重新运行。等等。参考元素target name。\r\n这里相对于原文增加了manifest标签，是要找到主类。执行java -jar Hello.jar控制台则输出hello world!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>注意的问题</h3>\r\n\r\n若系统环境变量里的CLASSPATH包含当前目录，即有\".\"值，则运行ant clean会出现\r\n<blockquote>BUILD FAILED\r\n[home]\\build.xml:24: Unable to delete file [home]\\hello.jar</blockquote>\r\n错误，删除系统环境变量CLASSPATH里的\".\"则可正常删除。解决办法来自<a href=\"https://issues.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=29066\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>和<a href=\"http://www.coderanch.com/t/108053/tools/unable-delete-or-rename-old\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。原因大致是文件被锁定无法删除。\r\n\r\n但是这就引发另外一个问题，命令行下执行java的文件需要带上-classpath参数。如\r\n<blockquote>\r\njavac Hello.java\r\njava -classpath . Hello\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n笔记至此，下回继续。','Ant学习笔记[1]','','publish','open','open','','ant-learning-1','','','2011-06-01 15:43:37','2011-06-01 07:43:37','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=426',0,'post','',2),(457,1,'2011-06-01 20:04:34','2011-06-01 12:04:34','linux虚拟机不能自动扩展磁盘大小，十分失望。于是只能想办法自己分进去。思路是：\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>在vmware扩大磁盘空间。</li>\r\n	<li>进入centos将扩大的空间分区出来。</li>\r\n	<li>格式化。</li>\r\n	<li>挂载到现有的挂载点上。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n首先关闭虚拟机，通过vmware外部分配给虚拟机磁盘空间10G，重启进入cent-os, fdisk /dev/sda命令新建分区，假设增加的分区是 /dev/sda4。创建分区的过程略去。创建分区完成提示重启，重启完成才能看见/dev/sda4。\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># mkfs.ext3 /dev/sda4\r\nmke2fs 1.39 (29-May-2006)\r\nFilesystem label=\r\nOS type: Linux\r\nBlock size=4096 (log=2)\r\nFragment size=4096 (log=2)\r\n1311552 inodes, 2622611 blocks\r\n131130 blocks (5.00%) reserved for the super user\r\nFirst data block=0\r\nMaximum filesystem blocks=2688548864\r\n81 block groups\r\n32768 blocks per group, 32768 fragments per group\r\n16192 inodes per group\r\nSuperblock backups stored on blocks: \r\n        32768, 98304, 163840, 229376, 294912, 819200, 884736, 1605632\r\n\r\nWriting inode tables: done                            \r\nCreating journal (32768 blocks): done\r\nWriting superblocks and filesystem accounting information: done\r\n\r\nThis filesystem will be automatically checked every 24 mounts or\r\n180 days, whichever comes first.  Use tune2fs -c or -i to override.\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># fdisk -l\r\n\r\nDisk /dev/sda: 32.2 GB, 32212254720 bytes\r\n255 heads, 63 sectors/track, 3916 cylinders\r\nUnits = cylinders of 16065 * 512 = 8225280 bytes\r\n\r\n   Device Boot      Start         End      Blocks   Id  System\r\n/dev/sda1   *           1          13      104391   83  Linux\r\n/dev/sda2              14        1305    10377990   8e  Linux LVM\r\n/dev/sda3            1306        2610    10482412+  8e  Linux LVM\r\n/dev/sda4            2611        3916    10490445   83  Linux\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># fdisk /dev/sda\r\n\r\nThe number of cylinders for this disk is set to 3916.\r\nThere is nothing wrong with that, but this is larger than 1024,\r\nand could in certain setups cause problems wit