     2611        3916    10490445   8e  Linux LVM\r\n\r\nCommand (m for help): w				      //写入\r\nThe partition table has been altered!\r\n\r\nCalling ioctl() to re-read partition table.\r\n\r\nWARNING: Re-reading the partition table failed with error 16: Device or resource busy.\r\nThe kernel still uses the old table.\r\nThe new table will be used at the next reboot.\r\nSyncing disks.\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n/--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># pvcreate /dev/sda4\r\n  Physical volume \"/dev/sda4\" successfully created\r\n\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># lvm\r\n\r\nlvm> pvscan\r\n  PV /dev/sda2   VG VolGroup00   lvm2 [9.88 GB / 0    free]\r\n  PV /dev/sda3   VG VolGroup00   lvm2 [9.97 GB / 928.00 MB free]\r\n  PV /dev/sda4                   lvm2 [10.00 GB]\r\n  Total: 3 [29.85 GB] / in use: 2 [19.84 GB] / in no VG: 1 [10.00 GB]         \r\n\r\nlvm> vgextend VolGroup00 /dev/sda4\r\n  Volume group \"VolGroup00\" successfully extended\r\n\r\nlvm> lvdisplay \r\n  --- Logical volume ---\r\n  LV Name                /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00\r\n  VG Name                VolGroup00\r\n  LV UUID                yLKSXD-7210-xbBV-BjpH-3Bnh-YTJR-skXRbQ\r\n  LV Write Access        read/write\r\n  LV Status              available\r\n  # open                 1\r\n  LV Size                17.00 GB\r\n  Current LE             544\r\n  Segments               2\r\n  Allocation             inherit\r\n  Read ahead sectors     auto\r\n  - currently set to     256\r\n  Block device           253:0\r\n   \r\n  --- Logical volume ---\r\n  LV Name                /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol01\r\n  VG Name                VolGroup00\r\n  LV UUID                EyfKKN-7AN9-YYlz-BrH4-xiiZ-I6fo-LX9N23\r\n  LV Write Access        read/write\r\n  LV Status              available\r\n  # open                 1\r\n  LV Size                1.94 GB\r\n  Current LE             62\r\n  Segments               1\r\n  Allocation             inherit\r\n  Read ahead sectors     auto\r\n  - currently set to     256\r\n  Block device           253:1\r\n   \r\nlvm> lvextend  -L+10G /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00\r\n  Extending logical volume LogVol00 to 27.00 GB\r\n  Logical volume LogVol00 successfully resized\r\n\r\nlvm> lvdisplay \r\n  --- Logical volume ---\r\n  LV Name                /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00\r\n  VG Name                VolGroup00\r\n  LV UUID                yLKSXD-7210-xbBV-BjpH-3Bnh-YTJR-skXRbQ\r\n  LV Write Access        read/write\r\n  LV Status              available\r\n  # open                 1\r\n  LV Size                27.00 GB\r\n  Current LE             864\r\n  Segments               3\r\n  Allocation             inherit\r\n  Read ahead sectors     auto\r\n  - currently set to     256\r\n  Block device           253:0\r\n   \r\n  --- Logical volume ---\r\n  LV Name                /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol01\r\n  VG Name                VolGroup00\r\n  LV UUID                EyfKKN-7AN9-YYlz-BrH4-xiiZ-I6fo-LX9N23\r\n  LV Write Access        read/write\r\n  LV Status              available\r\n  # open                 1\r\n  LV Size                1.94 GB\r\n  Current LE             62\r\n  Segments               1\r\n  Allocation             inherit\r\n  Read ahead sectors     auto\r\n  - currently set to     256\r\n  Block device           253:1\r\n\r\nlvm> exit\r\n  Exiting.\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n/--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n<blockquote>								  \r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># df						   //逻辑卷的大小已经更改到27G了，但文件系统仍没有增加\r\nFilesystem           1K-blocks      Used Available Use% Mounted on   \r\n/dev/mapper/VolGroup00-LogVol00\r\n                      17271868  11345240   5038732  70% /\r\n/dev/sda1               101086     11885     83982  13% /boot\r\ntmpfs                   517644         0    517644   0% /dev/shm\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># resize2fs /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00 		   //使用resize2fs命令将文件系统扩展到增加的空间上\r\nresize2fs 1.39 (29-May-2006)\r\nFilesystem at /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00 is mounted on /; on-line resizing required\r\nPerforming an on-line resize of /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00 to 7077888 (4k) blocks.\r\nThe filesystem on /dev/VolGroup00/LogVol00 is now 7077888 blocks long.\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>[root@localhost /]</strong># df -lh					  //查看文件系统\r\nFilesystem            Size  Used Avail Use% Mounted on\r\n/dev/mapper/VolGroup00-LogVol00\r\n                       27G   11G   14G  44% /\r\n/dev/sda1              99M   12M   83M  13% /boot\r\ntmpfs                 506M     0  506M   0% /dev/shm\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n\r\n至此结束。本文主要参考<a href=\"http://www.cnitblog.com/201/archive/2011/05/27/74088.html\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a>。','vmware虚拟机下cent-os追加磁盘空间','','publish','open','open','','vmware-add-disk-in-cent-os','','','2011-06-01 21:27:02','2011-06-01 13:27:02','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=457',0,'post','',1),(463,1,'2011-06-01 23:13:53','2011-06-01 15:13:53','首先必须要承认，自己真的太水太水了。不懂oracle，不懂ant，不懂ssh... 所有这些，都是听过没学，现在现学现用，现学不够用。于是我真的很该好好反省反思跪地板，不，应该跪主板...\r\n\r\n反过来回头记录小个过程。\r\n\r\n首先是远程主机。ssh确实很简单，一看就会。只是需要创建工作之后分配一台虚拟机的IP，之后登录到这个虚拟机远程调试所给的工程。\r\n\r\n所给工程使用Java+ant，于是我简单看了下ant，知道它就是makefile。还<a href=\"https://favorbook.com/2011/05/28/ant-learning-1/\" target=\"_blank\">笔记了一下</a>。只是之前都在eclipse下水一水的我完全没想那么多移植性的内容，更没想过如此大的工程的部署问题。于是对于这种build.xml都有上万行的工程不知所措。我只知道在1000+行出现了编译错误。于是我只好请教gDev的人了。\r\n\r\n之后我简单看了下oracle，打算在Windows下面搭建oracle，失败告终。个儿太大，安装速度慢，设置麻烦，机器带不起来，于是我就放弃了。学了几行命令，可是现在连怎么创建数据库都没整明白，更不用说什么instance之类的了。 不过话说回来oracle不愧是当之无愧的甲骨文，甲骨文就是生活在甲骨文时代的人才能懂的，因此得出结论干这行的都生活在那时代去了（当然这仅仅是个玩笑）。结构的复杂程度远远比SQL语法复杂得多，权限的设置更体现了甲骨文的甲骨文似的复杂。\r\n\r\n与gDev的人交流开始十分不畅，也许是我根本就存在于一个被不屑的角色，我不得不承认我本来就是这个角色。对于整个工程根本就没有任何了解并且也没有任何说明文档的前提下，只有几大页乱了顺序的编译依赖说明以及数据库搭建的依赖关系，我就十分朦胧的把责任推给了他们自己的源码有问题。直到得到他们的回复之后我发现原来要做那么些修改和依赖，但是这些修改确实在之前几页的混乱中体现出来了的。也不知道是我自己思路的问题还是其他，反正我猜测oracle数据库用户名和密码就花了老长时间。\r\n\r\n之后我就开始编译。好不容易编译成功了一次，之后将编译出来的.war文件发布到Tomcat下。通过ssh连接的远程主机，重启tomcat即可解压.war，但是怎么访问？浏览器直接进去？此法仅仅成功过1次。之后页面显示被重置，于是我知道我该感谢和崇拜我们伟大的墙了。直至今天，还是没有连接成功。\r\n\r\n我不确定是不是我用的源码的版本的错误，于是我决定重新编译。然后各种错误有接踵而至，oracle数据库依赖、环境配置、权限，之后遇到一个我无法解决的问题：远程主机磁盘空间30G写满了。我删除了很多内容，依然不够，oracle的sys用户连接不上磁盘空间不足，编译提示磁盘空间不可写。查看挂载在centos下的磁盘驱动器，欲新追加磁盘空间到远程主机，但是这种操作似乎需要重启，那如果远程主机动态分配IP岂不是我就完全ssh不上它了。于是我放弃了这种办法。\r\n\r\n剩下的办法，把远程主机的内容环境数据库内容拷贝到本地主机，在本地主机重新编译。至今没有成功，不知道哪个步骤出了问题。其中还出现了一个问题，本地虚拟机centos也磁盘空间不够了。我花了一个下午来解决这个没有什么技术难度的问题。当然也<a href=\"https://favorbook.com/2011/06/01/vmware-add-disk-in-cent-os/\" target=\"_blank\">笔记了一下</a>。现在还有一个最后的路，成功过1次的.war文件拷贝到本地之后，今天通过先drop掉某个oracle用户重新导入数据之后，竟然tomcat解压成功并且成功登录了。查看了下，竟然是一个工资管理系统，相当庞大。如此庞然大物竟然要我来test，我受宠若惊并且鸭梨很大。毕设在即，英语课还要party。\r\n\r\n博主，明天要加油了！','简单记录到目前还没战胜的挫折','','publish','open','open','','recent-days-frustration-cry','','https://favorbook.com/2011/05/28/ant-learning-1/\nhttps://favorbook.com/2011/06/01/vmware-add-disk-in-cent-os/','2011-06-02 09:20:40','2011-06-02 01:20:40','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=463',0,'post','',1),(1212,1,'2012-06-05 17:31:07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','http://heikezhi.com/2011/09/12/int-min-in-c/\r\n\r\nhttp://blog.regehr.org/archives/721','C integer','','draft','open','open','','','','','2012-06-05 17:31:07','2012-06-05 09:31:07','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1212',0,'post','',0),(475,1,'2011-06-02 23:54:24','2011-06-02 15:54:24','也许是<a href=\"http://www.vmware.com/\" target=\"_blank\">VMware</a>和<a href=\"http://www.vmlite.com/\" target=\"_blank\">VMLite</a>的冲突，造成在Windows 7 下面还存在VMware的情况下卸载VMLite蓝屏3次。于是我放弃正常卸载了。\r\n\r\n换到Ubuntu下，挂载Windows 7的系统盘，进入它的根目录\r\n<blockquote>find . -name \"*VMLite*\"</blockquote>\r\n之后将所有列表的全部删除:\r\n<blockquote>rm -rf ××</blockquote>\r\n文件较多，可以写一个脚本自动删除，切换到Linux下为了能最高权限删除文件。包括已存在的一个XP Mode，大致文件目录有：\r\n<blockquote>./ProgramData/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation\r\n./ProgramData/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation/VMLite command prompt.lnk\r\n./ProgramData/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation/VMLite Wizard.lnk\r\n./ProgramData/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation/VMLite Workstation.lnk\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Local/VMLite Workstation\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Local/VMLite Workstation/VMLite XP Mode\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Internet Explorer/Quick Launch/VMLite Workstation.lnk\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation/VMLite XP Mode Applications\r\n./Users/Wayne/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/VMLite Workstation/VMLite XP Mode.lnk\r\n./Users/Wayne/VMLites\r\n./Windows/System32/drivers/VMLiteUSB.sys\r\n./Windows/System32/DriverStore/FileRepository/vmliteusb.inf_x86_neutral_7d6e765a65db7208/VMLiteUSB.cat\r\n./Windows/System32/DriverStore/FileRepository/vmliteusb.inf_x86_neutral_7d6e765a65db7208/VMLiteUSB.inf\r\n./Windows/System32/DriverStore/FileRepository/vmliteusb.inf_x86_neutral_7d6e765a65db7208/VMLiteUSB.sys</blockquote>\r\n删除之后清理下注册表，进入设备管理器卸载VMLite的虚拟网卡，删除VMLite的服务，至此结束。','Windows7卸载VMLite蓝屏','','publish','open','open','','uninstall-vmware-at-window7','','','2011-06-03 17:54:14','2011-06-03 09:54:14','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=475',0,'post','',0),(568,1,'2011-06-13 20:39:38','2011-06-13 12:39:38','某Web Service发布到Tomcat下，运行客户端发现小测试集可以通过，但是大测试集时候内存溢出了。于是寻找增加JVM内存的办法。参考<a href=\"http://hi.baidu.com/coolcat_police/blog/item/66796fef6f51831ffcfa3c77.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。摘抄如下：\r\n<blockquote>\r\n如果你是使用start.bat脚本启动的话，请打开catalina.bat，在最前面添加：\r\nset JAVA_OPTS=-Xms512m -Xmx512m\r\n\r\n如果你是使用service启动的话，请打开regedit编辑注册表：\r\nHKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Apache Software Foundation\\Procrun 2.0\\Tomcat6\\Parameters\\Java\r\n找到叫做Options的key，打开可以看到：\r\n-Dcatalina.home=C:\\Program Files\\Apache Software Foundation\\Tomcat 6.0\r\n-Dcatalina.base=C:\\Program Files\\Apache Software Foundation\\Tomcat 6.0\r\n-Djava.endorsed.dirs=C:\\Program Files\\Apache Software Foundation\\Tomcat 6.0\\endorsed\r\n-Djava.io.tmpdir=C:\\Program Files\\Apache Software Foundation\\Tomcat 6.0\\temp\r\n-Djava.util.logging.manager=org.apache.juli.ClassLoaderLogManager\r\n-Djava.util.logging.config.file=C:\\Program Files\\Apache Software Foundation\\Tomcat 6.0\\conf\\logging.properties\r\n\r\n请在最下面添加：\r\n-Xms512m -Xmx512m\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n若是从MyEclipse启动Tomcat，则preference-MyEclipse-Application Services-Tomcat-Tomcat 6.x-JDK处添加参数：\r\n<blockquote>-Xms512m -Xmx512m</blockquote>\r\n\r\n或者preference-java-instal jres-edit增加参数：\r\n<blockquote>-Xms512m -Xmx512m</blockquote>\r\n\r\n重启Tomcat，之后打开<a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/manager/status\">http://127.0.0.1:8080/manager/status</a>即可看见JVM内存有增加了：\r\n<blockquote>JVM\r\nFree memory: 415.25 MB Total memory: 494.93 MB Max memory: 494.93 MB</blockquote>\r\n\r\n','增加Windows下Tomcat 6的JVM内存','','publish','open','open','','windows-tomcat-6-add-jvm-mem','','','2011-06-13 20:57:47','2011-06-13 12:57:47','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=568',0,'post','',0),(545,1,'2011-06-06 14:21:06','2011-06-06 06:21:06','在访问Tomcat的8080端口时，发现访问不了。修改D:\\Tomcat 6.0\\conf\\sever.xml 端口配置为8001，通过http://localhost:8001可以访问，于是确定8080被某程序占用了。命令：\r\n<blockquote>netstat -aon|findstr \"8080\"\r\n  TCP    0.0.0.0:8080           0.0.0.0:0              LISTENING       2124\r\n</blockquote>\r\n之后再：\r\n<blockquote>\r\ntasklist|findstr \"2124\"\r\n</blockquote>\r\n即可查看占用此端口的程序。\r\n\r\n之后就该怎么解决就怎么解决了。','Windows查看某端口被什么程序占用','','publish','open','open','','lookup-port-pid','','','2011-06-06 14:21:07','2011-06-06 06:21:07','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=545',0,'post','',0),(549,1,'2011-06-06 20:11:09','2011-06-06 12:11:09','开始参考IBM的<a href=\"http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/java/j-lo-xfire/\" target=\"_blank\">轻松将 POJO 发布成 Web 服务</a>。之后参考<a href=\"http://www.zjsyc.com/blog/article/java/Java_XFire_WebService.html\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a>，最后遇到的错误参考<a href=\"http://liyege2003.it