4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1737,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:17','2013-04-04 02:16:17',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1737','','','2015-02-04 19:23:56','2015-02-04 11:23:56','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1737',15,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1738,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:18','2013-04-04 02:16:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1738','','','2015-02-04 19:23:57','2015-02-04 11:23:57','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1738',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1739,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:19','2013-04-04 02:16:19',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1739','','','2015-02-04 19:23:58','2015-02-04 11:23:58','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1739',17,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1740,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:20','2013-04-04 02:16:20',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1740','','','2015-02-04 19:23:59','2015-02-04 11:23:59','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1740',18,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1741,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:22','2013-04-04 02:16:22',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1741','','','2015-02-04 19:24:00','2015-02-04 11:24:00','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1741',19,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1742,1,'2013-04-04 10:16:23','2013-04-04 02:16:23',' ','','','publish','open','open','','1742','','','2015-02-04 19:24:01','2015-02-04 11:24:01','',154,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1742',20,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1764,1,'2013-04-08 14:10:05','2013-04-08 06:10:05','实际上本博客的访问量相当小，完全不足以采用什么优化的策略，默认就完全可以顶得住了。但是鄙人还是那么瞎折腾，于是也进行了一番优化，虽然表面看上去速度提升不大，也算寻求点心理安慰。\r\n\r\n<h3>启用Gzip压缩</h3>\r\n\r\ngzip压缩很简单，直接在wordpress的安装目录下.htaccess中写入：\r\n<code>RewriteEngine on\r\n# Gzip\r\n&lt;ifmodule mod_deflate.c&gt;\r\nAddOutputFilter DEFLATE html xml php js css\r\n&lt;/ifmodule&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n之后在<a href=\"http://tool.chinaz.com/Gzips/\" target=\"_blank\">站长工具</a>检测网站是否开启Gzip压缩。\r\n\r\n<h3>缓存</h3>\r\n\r\n缓存使用<a href=\"http://www.storyday.com/tag/cos-html-cache\" target=\"_blank\">cos-html-cache</a>插件，只需要将wordpress的固定链接设置为 /%postname%.html，它会在 wordpress 的安装目录下缓存 .html 文件。\r\n\r\n我用的是Windows主机，IIS 6.0，在这里无法使用html压缩，具体原因我也不懂。于是对我的缓存来说，同时有优缺点：\r\n\r\n<blockquote>优点：不缓存每次访问需要查询数据库大约耗时0.5秒，缓存则可以减少这段时间；\r\n缺点：无法压缩，增加网络流量。大约每个.html文件本来可以从30KB压缩到6KB左右；</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<h3>启用CDN</h3>\r\n\r\nCDN是什么可以看<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Content_delivery_network\" target=\"_blank\">维基百科</a>，其具体的设置步骤：\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>在安全保的管理页面增加域名设置：\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/anquanbao-vnnii.jpg\" alt=\"anquanbao-vnnii\" width=\"960\" height=\"192\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1770\" /></li>\r\n	<li>在<a href=\"https://www.dnspod.cn\" target=\"_blank\">DNSPOD</a>增加域名解析，增加CNAME记录指向安全保分配的CNAME服务域名。\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/dnspod-vnnii.jpg\" alt=\"dnspod-vnnii\" width=\"778\" height=\"175\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1771\" /></li>\r\n        \r\n	<li>将以上3个子域名js.vnnii.com, css.vnnii.com, img.vnnii.com 都绑定到虚拟主机空间与wordpress根目录，使得通过例如<a href=\"http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg</a>地址可以访问到wp-content下的图片等文件。不同的主机商不同的操作，这里不再叙述。</li>\r\n\r\n        <li>在wordpress后台使用<a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/autoptimize/\" target=\"_blank\">Autoptimize</a>插件，将 img.vnnii.com, js.vnnii.com, css.vnnii.com 作为CDN加速。设置可以看图所示。\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/autoptimize-settings-cdn.jpg\" alt=\"autoptimize-settings-cdn\" width=\"775\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1769\" /</li>\r\n\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n由于我的 vnnii.com 域名在国内已经备案，因此可以使用一些免费的国内CDN进行加速，例如<a href=\"http://anquanbao.com/\" target=\"_blank\">安全保</a>，<a href=\"http://www.jiasule.com/\" target=\"_blank\">加速乐</a>，<a href=\"https://www.cdnzz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">CDNZZ</a> 都有免费版本。我简单<a href=\"http://ping.chinaz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">多个地点ping服务器</a>来测试了下安全保和加速乐，发现安全保的加速效果好一点，可能是因为它的结点多一些。\r\n\r\n以上为什么使用3个子域名分别对js，css，img进行加速是因为安全保对于一个记录只有10MB的缓存空间，因此把它们分开可以缓存多一些。\r\n\r\n<h3>移除Admin Bar</h3>\r\nAdmin Bar在登录的时候访问页面都显示，看着实在不爽，于是参考<a href=\"http://www.wprecipes.com/how-to-remove-wordpress-3-1-admin-bar\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>将它移除。最简单的在主题的functions.php里面加上：\r\n<code>/* Remove Admin Bar*/\r\nshow_admin_bar( false );</code>','Wordpress优化(压缩、缓存、CDN)','','publish','open','open','','wordpress-optimized-with-compression-caching-cdn','','','2013-04-08 20:26:27','2013-04-08 12:26:27','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1764',0,'post','',0),(1775,1,'2013-04-08 13:53:47','2013-04-08 05:53:47','在<a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/zh-cn:%E5%B0%86_WordPress_%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%BD%AE%E4%BA%8E%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%AD%90%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95\" target=\"_blank\">这里(中文)</a>和<a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Giving_WordPress_Its_Own_Directory\" target=\"_blank\">这里(英文)</a>介绍了将wordpress安装到子目录的其中一个方法，但是这个方法会在虚拟主机根目录占用index.php文件，于是想寻求另外的方法。\r\n\r\n可以通过修改.htaccess来实现。\r\n<h3>方法1(有问题)</h3>\r\n在虚拟主机根目录下增加：\r\n<code># Sub dir blog|content|img|js|css.vnnii.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?blog|content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/wordpress/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /wordpress/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?blog|content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ wordpress/c.html\r\n</code>\r\n那么 blog.vnnii.com, content.vnnii.com, img.vnnii.com, js.vnnii.com, css.vnnii.com 都被指向了 ./wordpress/ 子目录。\r\n\r\n原本 wordpress 子目录下的 .htaccess 内容为：\r\n<code># BEGIN WordPress\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine On\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteRule ^index\\.php$ - [L]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php [L]\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n# END WordPress\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n这样在我的Windows主机上会有问题，通过类似<a href=\"http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg</a>无法访问，会跳转到<a href=\"http://luckyet.com\" target=\"_blank\">我的首页</a>。而wordpress固定链接却变为类似于<a href=\"https://favorbook.com/index.php/download-gmail-app.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://favorbook.com/index.php/download-gmail-app.html</a>这样的链接，多了一个index.php，丑得不得了。至今我Google了半天仍然没找到可以解决我的问题的办法。\r\n<h3>方法2(问题半解决)</h3>\r\n在虚拟主机根目录下增加：\r\n<code># Sub dir content|img|js|css.vnnii.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/wordpress/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /wordpress/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ wordpress/c.html\r\n</code>\r\n即去掉 blog.vnnii.com, 将 content.vnnii.com, img.vnnii.com, js.vnnii.com, css.vnnii.com 指向 ./wordpress/ 子目录。而 blog.vnnii.com 通过虚拟主机提供商的控制面板绑定到子目录 wordpress (<a href=\"http://www.ewsidc.com/hostingtw.htm\" target=\"_blank\">EWSIDC TW-1000A</a>只能绑定1个子空间)。\r\n\r\n在 wordpress 子目录下的 .htaccess 内容增加一行，即为：\r\n<code># BEGIN WordPress\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine On\r\nRewriteBase /\r\n# 当访问的是index.php时则不进行重定向\r\nRewriteRule ^index\\.php$ - [L]\r\n# 当访问的域名是 blog.vnnii.com 才进行重定向\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^favorbook.com [NC]\r\n# 如果文件存在，就直接访问文件，不进行下面的RewriteRule\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\n# 如果目录存在，就直接访问目录，不进行下面的RewriteRule\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php [L]\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n# END WordPress\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n这样就可通过类似<a href=\"http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.vnnii.com/wp-content/themes/skirmish/img/header.jpg</a>访问下面的图片，css，javascript文件，缺点是无法通过<a href=\"http://img.vnnii.com/download-gmail-app.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.vnnii.com/download-gmail-app.html</a>访问具体文章(如果你测试到这篇文章能访问，那是cos-html-cache插件生成的缓存)。\r\n<h3>我的.htaccess备份</h3>\r\n根目录：\r\n<code>RewriteEngine on\r\n# Sub dir vnnii.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?blog.vnnii\\.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/vnnii.com/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /vnnii.com/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?blog.vnnii\\.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ vnnii.com/index.php\r\n# Sub dir tw.luckyet.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?tw.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/tw.luckyet.com/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /tw.luckyet.com/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?tw.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ tw.luckyet.com/index.html\r\n# Sub dir img.luckyet.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?img.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/images/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /images/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?img.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ images/index.html\r\n# Sub dir tools.luckyet.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?tools.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/tools/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /tools/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?tools.luckyet.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ tools/index.html\r\n# Sub dir content.vnnii.com\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/wordpress/\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ /wordpress/$1\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^(www\\.)?content|img|css|js.vnnii.com$ [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(/)?$ wordpress/c.html\r\n# 301\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^vnnii.com [NC,OR]\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^www.vnnii.com [NC,OR]\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^www.luckyet.com [NC]\r\nRewriteRule ^(.*)$ http://luckyet.com/$1 [R=301]\r\n# 404\r\nErrorDocument 404 /404.html\r\n# Gzip\r\n&lt;ifmodule mod_deflate.c&gt;\r\nAddOutputFilter DEFLATE html xml php js css\r\n&lt;/ifmodule&gt;\r\nFileETag none\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_expires.c&gt;\r\n# Enable expirations\r\nExpiresActive On\r\n# Default directive\r\nExpiresDefault \"access plus 1 month\"\r\n# My favicon\r\nExpiresByType image/x-icon \"access plus 1 year\"\r\n# Images\r\nExpiresByType image/gif \"access plus 1 month\"\r\nExpiresByType image/png \"access plus 1 month\"\r\nExpiresByType image/jpg \"access plus 1 month\"\r\nExpiresByType image/jpeg \"access plus 1 month\"\r\n# CSS\r\nExpiresByType text/css \"access 1 month\"\r\n# Javascript\r\nExpiresByType application/javascript \"access plus 1 year\"\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n</code>\r\nwordpress 目录：\r\n<code>RewriteEngine on\r\n# Gzip\r\n&lt;ifmodule mod_deflate.c&gt;\r\nAddOutputFilter DEFLATE html xml php js css\r\n&lt;/ifmodule&gt;\r\n# 404\r\nErrorDocument 404 /404.html\r\nFileETag none\r\n# 1 YEAR\r\n&lt;FilesMatch \"\\.(ico|pdf|flv)$\"&gt;\r\nHeader set Cache-Control \"max-age=29030400, public\"\r\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;\r\n# 1 WEEK\r\n&lt;FilesMatch \"\\.(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|swf)$\"&gt;\r\nHeader set Cache-Control \"max-age=604800, public\"\r\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;\r\n# 2 DAYS\r\n&lt;FilesMatch \"\\.(xml|txt|css|js)$\"&gt;\r\nHeader set Cache-Control \"max-age=172800, proxy-revalidate\"\r\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;\r\n# 1 MIN\r\n&lt;FilesMatch \"\\.(html|htm|php)$\"&gt;\r\nHeader set Cache-Control \"max-age=60, private, proxy-revalidate\"\r\n&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;\r\n# BEGIN WordPress\r\n&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;\r\nRewriteEngine On\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteRule ^index\\.php$ - [L]\r\nRewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^favorbook.com [NC]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d\r\nRewriteRule . /index.php [L]\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt;\r\n# END WordPress\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<h3>问题</h3>\r\n若有人知道如何去掉Windows虚拟主机，IIS 6.0安装 wordpress 到子目录时出现的固定链接中的 index.php 的话，留言告知，我将不甚感激。','设置.htaccess将子域名绑定到wordpress根目录','','publish','open','open','','giving_wordpress_its_own_directory','','\nhttps://favorbook.com/index.php/download-gmail-app.html','2013-04-08 13:55:36','2013-04-08 05:55:36','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1775',0,'post','',0),(1782,1,'2013-04-08 14:06:20','2013-04-08 06:06:20','本来<a href=\"http://fayaa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">发芽网</a>是可以提供代码高亮直接生成html代码，但是还是不是很好看，我还是比较喜欢看简洁的，即使没有高亮功能。\r\n\r\n于是我看到了<a href=\"http://onedou.com/archives/643.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>，正是我想要的效果。抄袭一下，增加到自己主题的 style.css 的最后，刷新下页面看下效果。\r\n\r\n看一下效果，这就是增加的CSS样式：\r\n<code>code {\r\n	text-indent:0;\r\n	border-color:#000;\r\n	border-style:dashed;\r\n	border-width:1px;\r\n	display:block;\r\n	font-size:12px;\r\n	font-family:Courier, Calibri,\"宋体\";\r\n	margin:10px 0 0 0;\r\n	padding:10px 0 10px 5px;\r\n	-moz-border-radius:5px;\r\n	background:#f5f5f5;\r\n	color:#000;\r\n}</code>\r\n\r\n需要注意的是大于号(&gt;)、小于号(&lt;) 等在wordpress普通的Text编辑器里面需要转义一下，转义为 &amp;gt; 或者 &amp;lt;','wordpress的code标签的css样式','','publish','open','open','','wordpress-code-css','','','2013-04-08 14:06:20','2013-04-08 06:06:20','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1782',0,'post','',0),(1872,1,'2013-04-09 18:48:29','2013-04-09 10:48:29','在我<a href=\"https://favorbook.com/usb-install-fedora-17-and-configuration.html\" target=\"_blank\">U盘安装Fedora 17及快速配置</a>中说明了安装fedora 17的快速配置，由于安装fedora 18采用的是live CD安装，因此不是太一样，重新记录一下。\r\n\r\n<h3>制作Fedora 18安装U盘</h3>\r\n同样，按照以往的步骤：\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>下载<a href=\"http://202.118.253.7/download/1049981/1054468/5/iso/118/214/1358547430006_982/Fedora-18-x86_64-Live-Desktop.iso\" target=\"_blank\">Fedora-18-x86_64-Live-Desktop.iso</a>；</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>下载<a href=\"https://fedorahosted.org/liveusb-creator/ \" target=\"_blank\">LiveUSB-Creator</a>，将Fedora-18-x86_64-Live-Desktop.iso写入U盘；</li>\r\n\r\n从U盘引导安装。</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>配置ssh server</h3>\r\n参考<a href=\"http://liumin20081128.blog.163.com/blog/static/60196069201172782954687/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>，大致步骤记录：\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>查看运行状态(To check if it is installed and running use the following command):\r\n<code>sudo /sbin/service sshd status </code></li>\r\n	<li>启动ssh server(If the service is installed, but not running, it can be started either from the command-line):\r\n<code>sudo /sbin/service sshd start</code></li>\r\n	<li>配置ssh\r\n打开/etc/ssh/ssh_config ，去掉其中：\r\n<code>Port 22\r\nProtocol 2,1</code>\r\n前面的#号，然后重新启动：<code>service sshd restart</code></li>\r\n	<li>配置开机自动启动SSH服务：\r\n<code>/sudo systemctl enable sshd.service </code>\r\n\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>设置防火墙，允许ssh端口被访问：\r\n<code>sudo iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -j ACCEPT</code>\r\n然后就可以通过ssh工具连接了。\r\n或者在图形界面下对防火墙进行配置，启动防火墙配置：\r\n<code>sudo /usr/bin/system-config-firewall</code></li>\r\n	<li>其它\r\nfedora与debain和unbutu一样，也可以通过下面命令进行启动与关闭：\r\n<code>/etc/init.d/sshd stop\r\n/etc/init.d/sshd start\r\n/etc/init.d/sshd restart\r\n/etc/init.d/iptables stop\r\n/etc/init.d/iptables start\r\nchkconfig sshd on</code></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n之所以要把配置ssh server放在前面，则后面的操作可以在其他机器上ssh到这台机器上操作，不必要在本机上操作。这在还没有安装synergy来说省掉一套鼠标键盘。\r\n\r\n<h3>源配置</h3>\r\n参考<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_69a3dde9010180bw.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。\r\n\r\n<h3>安装vim,gcc,git及配置</h3>\r\n安装\r\n<code>sudo yum install vim gcc git</code>\r\n下载vim配置，我的在<a href=\"https://github.com/zweecn/vim\" target=\"_blank\">github</a>可以下载zip包，也可以fork到你自己的仓库。解压到~/目录。\r\n<code>wget https://nodeload.github.com/zweecn/vim/zip/master -O vim-master.zip\r\nunzip vim-master.zip\r\nmv vim-master .vim\r\nmv .vim ~/\r\ncp .vim/vimrc .vimrc</code>\r\n如果打开vi发现没有ctags，那么安装：\r\n<code>wget http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/ctags/ctags/5.8/ctags-5.8.tar.gz\r\ntar -zxvf ctags-5.8.tar.gz\r\ncd ctags-5.8\r\n./configure\r\nmake\r\nsudo make install</code>\r\n\r\n<h3>安装synergy</h3>\r\nsynergy是多台电脑共用鼠标键盘的，可以在<a href=\"http://synergy-foss.org/zh-cn/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>去下载rpm包，之后\r\n<code>sudo rpm -ivh *.rpm\r\nsynergy</code>\r\n弹出界面后设置自动启动，客户端还是服务器按情况设置。\r\n\r\n其余的参考<a href=\"https://favorbook.com/usb-install-fedora-17-and-configuration.html\" target=\"_blank\">U盘安装Fedora 17及快速配置</a>','U盘安装Fedora 18及快速配置','','publish','open','open','','usb-install-fedora-18-and-configuration','','\nhttps://favorbook.com/usb-install-fedora-17-and-configuration.html','2013-04-09 18:48:29','2013-04-09 10:48:29','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1872',0,'post','',0),(1887,1,'2013-04-09 20:31:40','2013-04-09 12:31:40','<a href=\"http://man.lupaworld.com/content/manage/ringkee/awk.htm\" target=\"_blank\">原文链接</a>。\r\n\r\n为了避免原文链接失效，我将原文保存到我的博客地址：<a href=\"http://luckyet.com/html/awk.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击进入</a>。','[转]awk学习笔记','','publish','open','open','','awk-learning','','','2013-04-09 20:31:40','2013-04-09 12:31:40','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1887',0,'post','',0),(1922,1,'2013-05-07 17:12:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','年轻还是老','','draft','open','open','','young-or-old','','','2013-05-07 17:12:59','2013-05-07 09:12:59','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=1922',0,'post','',0),(1891,1,'2013-04-16 21:38:14','2013-04-16 13:38:14','需要实现一个功能，C++程序中调用Matlab。例如，当用C++做实验跑出一些数据，想要放到Matlab里画图的时候，如果重新用matlab写画图就比较麻烦，于是在C++里将数据处理好后直接传到Matlab画图即可。\r\n<h3>环境配置</h3>\r\n在写程序之前需要配置环境，VS下的依赖比较方便，网上一大堆。可以参考<a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/andavid/archive/2011/12/02/2272281.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。但是QtCreator的就比较少了，可以参考<a href=\"http://michael-stengel.com/blog/?p=89\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。简单记录下。\r\n<h4>VS中环境配置</h4>\r\n右键点击工程，Project Properties-&gt;Configuration Properties-&gt;VC++ Directories-&gt;Include Directories 增加：\r\n<code>E:\\Programs\\Matlab2011x86\\extern\\include</code>\r\nProject Properties-&gt;Configuration Properties-&gt;VC++ Directories-&gt;Library Directories 增加：\r\n<code>E:\\Programs\\Matlab2011x86\\extern\\lib\\win32\\microsoft\\msvc71</code>\r\n具体路径各个安装不一样。\r\n<h4>QtCreator中环境配置</h4>\r\nThe project setup is pretty simple. Go into your .pro file and add\r\n<code>INCLUDEPATH += E:\\Programs\\Matlab2011x86\\extern\\include\r\nLIBS += -L E:\\Programs\\Matlab2011x86\\extern\\lib\\win32\\microsoft\\msvc71 -llibeng -llibmat -llibmx</code>\r\n<h3>测试程序</h3>\r\n只在QtCreator中测试，VS的网上太多，不必测试了。\r\nMatlabTest.pro\r\n<code>QT += core gui\r\nTA