w.google.com.hk;\r\n	}\r\n}</code>\r\n\r\n然后service nginx restart重启服务器。打开浏览器访问就可以了。\r\n\r\n特别注意，如果出现“”错误，参考这篇文章：<a href=\"https://my.oschina.net/AliMobileSecurity/blog/755304\" target=\"_blank\">Android安全开发之安全使用HTTPS</a>\r\n\r\n即生成key的过程中，<strong>Common Name必须和网站域名一致，以便之后进行Host Name校验</strong>\r\n\r\n步骤截几个图放在下面备忘一下。\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ssl-key1.jpeg\" alt=\"ssl-key1\" width=\"898\" height=\"1060\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2157\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ssl-key2.jpeg\" alt=\"ssl-key2\" width=\"898\" height=\"1060\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2158\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://favorbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ssl-key3.jpeg\" alt=\"ssl-key3\" width=\"898\" height=\"1060\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2159\" />','vps搭建Google的反向代理并启用SSL','','inherit','closed','closed','','2156-revision-v1','','','2016-11-24 19:45:54','2016-11-24 11:45:54','',2156,'https://favorbook.com/2156-revision-v1.html',0,'revision','',0),(2164,1,'2016-11-24 20:11:26','2016-11-24 12:11:26','试了好多种Google的反向代理，还是这种最方便，即安装nginx时多加一个模块，配置一行就可以反向代理了。\r\n\r\n源码和方法来自这里：<a href=\"https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module</a> 以下截取部分重要步骤。\r\n\r\n<h3>升级nginx</h3>\r\n<code>cd /root/pkg\r\ngit clone https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module\r\ngit clone https://github.com/yaoweibin/ngx_http_substitutions_filter_module\r\nwget http://soft.vpser.net/lnmp/lnmp1.3-full.tar.gz\r\ntar -zxvf lnmp1.3-full.tar.gz\r\ncd lnmp1.3-full\r\nvi lnmp.conf</code>\r\n将以上2个模块加到编译选项中，即\r\n<code>Nginx_Modules_Options=\'--add-module=/root/pkg/ngx_http_google_filter_module --add-module=/root/pkg/ngx_http_substitutions_filter_module\'</code>\r\n执行升级脚本：\r\n<code>./upgrade.sh nginx 1.10.22</code>\r\n以上，把nginx升级到了1.10.22版本。\r\n\r\n<h3>安装SSL证书</h3>\r\n特别注意要把openssl升级一下，最好直接用yum安装升级，可以换一个源之后升级。可参考这里换上163的源：<a href=\"http://mirrors.163.com/.help/centos.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://mirrors.163.com/.help/centos.html</a>\r\n\r\n<code>mv /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.backup\r\nwget http://mirrors.163.com/.help/CentOS7-Base-163.repo\r\nyum clean all\r\nyum makecache\r\nyum install openssl</code>\r\n\r\n安装Let\'s Encrypt SSL的方法来自这里：<a href=\"https://github.com/diafygi/acme-tiny\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/diafygi/acme-tiny</a> 也以看中文翻译版版：<a href=\"https://imququ.com/post/letsencrypt-certificate.html\" target=\"_blank\">Let\'s Encrypt，免费好用的 HTTPS 证书</a>。具体步骤如下：\r\n<code>openssl genrsa 4096 > account.key\r\nopenssl genrsa 4096 > domain.key\r\nopenssl req -new -sha256 -key domain.key -subj \"/\" -reqexts SAN -config <(cat /etc/pki/tls/openssl.cnf <(printf \"[SAN]\\nsubjectAltName=DNS:favorbook.com,DNS:go.favorbook.com,DNS:www.favorbook.com,DNS:lucker.me,DNS:go.lucker.me,DNS:www.lucker.me\")) > domain.csr\r\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/diafygi/acme-tiny/master/acme_tiny.py --no-check-certificate\r\npython acme_tiny.py --account-key ./account.key --csr ./domain.csr --acme-dir /home/wwwroot/challenges/ > ./signed.crt\r\nwget -O - https://letsencrypt.org/certs/lets-encrypt-x3-cross-signed.pem > intermediate.pem\r\ncat signed.crt intermediate.pem > chained.pem\r\nwget -O - https://letsencrypt.org/certs/isrgrootx1.pem > root.pem\r\ncat intermediate.pem root.pem > full_chained.pem</code>\r\n\r\n然后再配制个crontab来自动续期。\r\n\r\n<h3>配置nginx</h3>\r\n<code>vim /usr/local/nginx/conf/vhost/lucker.me.conf</code>\r\n直接贴配置了：\r\n<code>upstream www.google.com {\r\n    server 74.125.200.102:443;\r\n    server 74.125.200.101:443;\r\n    server 74.125.200.100:443;\r\n    server 74.125.200.138:443;\r\n    server 74.125.200.113:443;\r\n    server 74.125.200.139:443;\r\n}\r\nserver\r\n{\r\n    listen 80;\r\n    server_name lucker.me www.lucker.me go.lucker.me encrypted.lucker.me;\r\n    rewrite ^(.*) https://lucker.me$1 permanent;\r\n}\r\nserver\r\n{\r\n    listen 443;\r\n    server_name www.lucker.me go.lucker.me encrypted.lucker.me;\r\n    rewrite ^(.*) https://lucker.me$1 permanent;\r\n}\r\nserver\r\n{\r\n    listen 443 ssl;\r\n    server_name lucker.me;\r\n    ssl on;\r\n    ssl_certificate /root/encrypt_ssl/chained.pem;\r\n    ssl_certificate_key /root/encrypt_ssl/domain.key;\r\n    ssl_protocols SSLv3 TLSv1;\r\n    ssl_ciphers ALL:-ADH:+HIGH:+MEDIUM:-LOW:-SSLv2:-EXP;\r\n    location /.well-known/acme-challenge/ {\r\n        alias /home/wwwroot/challenges/;\r\n        try_files $uri =404;\r\n    }\r\n    resolver 8.8.8.8;\r\n    location / {\r\n        google on;\r\n        google_language zh-CN;\r\n    }\r\n}</code>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','升级lnmp里的nginx支持sub_filter','','publish','open','open','','update-lnmp-nginx-to-use-sub-filter','','','2016-11-24 20:12:16','2016-11-24 12:12:16','',0,'https://favorbook.com/?p=2164',0,'post','',0),(2165,1,'2016-11-24 19:59:51','2016-11-24 11:59:51','试了好多种Google的反向代理，还是这种最方便，即安装nginx时多加一个模块，配置一行就可以反向代理了。\r\n\r\n源码和方法来自这里：<a href=\"https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module</a> 以下截取部分重要步骤。\r\n\r\n<h3>升级nginx</h3>\r\n<code>cd /root/pkg\r\ngit clone https://github.com/cuber/ngx_http_google_filter_module\r\ngit clone https://github.com/yaoweibin/ngx_http_substitutions_filter_module\r\nwget http://soft.vpser.net/lnmp/lnmp1.3-full.tar.gz\r\ntar -zxvf lnmp1.3-full.tar.gz\r\ncd lnmp1.3-full\r\nvi lnmp.conf</code>\r\n将以上2个模块加到编译选项中，即\r\n<code>Nginx_Modules_Options=\'--add-module=/root/pkg/ngx_http_google_filter_module --add-module=/root/pkg/ngx_http_substitutions_filter_module\'</code>\r\n执行升级脚本：\r\n<code>./upgrade.sh nginx 1.10.22</code>\r\n以上，把nginx升级到了1.10.22版本。\r\n\r\n\r\n安装Let\'s Encrypt SSL的方法来自这里：<a href=\"https://github.com/diafygi/acme-tiny\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/diafygi/acme-tiny</a> 也以看中文翻译版版：<a href=\"https://imququ.com/post/letsencrypt-certificate.html\" target=\"_blank\">L